 688:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/core/lv_obj_style.c **** /**
 689:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/core/lv_obj_style.c ****  * Get the local style of an object for a given part and for a given state.
